Class ServiceParameterExample

java.lang.Object
  examples.ServiceParameterExample

public class ServiceParameterExample
extends java.lang.Object

This example shows how to access Profile.getServiceParameters() and Profile.getCategories() values. Different reasoners will provide different information depending on their capabilities. When there is no reasoner associated with the KB, no information about some profile can be retrieved because it cannot be verified that profile is actually an instance of profile:Profile concept. If strict type checking is disabled (see OWLKnowledgeBase.setStrictConversion(boolean)) then some information can be retrieved.
